title: Cartoon Donald Trump's Phone Call With Australia's PM Doesn't Go As Planned
text:
Cartoon Donald Trump's Phone Call With Australia's PM Doesn't Go As Planned “Your country’s a giant desert full of jumping rats." 02/03/2017 05:11 am ET Lee Moran Trends Editor, The Huffington Post President Donald Trump’s telephone conversation with Australian Prime Minister Malcolm Turnbull reportedly didn’t end well last weekend. Cartoon Trump’s call down under doesn’t go as planned either in this “ Late Show ” spoof.
